[normal]48.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]The Government has also supported the establishment of 
[normal]the 
[normal]UK CCS Research Centre
[normal] (UKCCSRC) – a 
[normal]c.
[normal]£13 million 
[normal]investment which
[normal] brings together th
